msgid ""
"Deploy Klein for Ray applications to an existing Ray cluster, Ray Jobs, "
"containers, and KubeRay."
msgstr "将 Klein for Ray 应用部署到现有 Ray 集群、Ray Jobs、容器和 KubeRay。"

msgid "Deploy Klein jobs"
msgstr "部署 Klein 作业"

msgid "A production deployment has three independent pieces:"
msgstr "生产部署包含三个独立部分："

msgid "a Ray cluster with enough worker resources and observability enabled;"
msgstr "具备足够 worker 资源且已启用可观测性的 Ray 集群；"

msgid ""
"an identical Python environment on every node that may run a Klein task;"
msgstr "每个可能运行 Klein 任务的节点上都有相同的 Python 环境；"

msgid ""
"a submission process that builds the graph, records the job namespace, and "
"exits or attaches without owning the job's lifetime."
msgstr "一个负责构建图、记录作业命名空间，然后退出或连接但不拥有作业生命周期的提交流程。"

msgid ""
"Klein's streaming JobManager is a named detached actor. Losing the "
"submitting process does not stop the job, but losing the whole Ray cluster "
"requires a new submission from durable checkpoint storage."
msgstr "Klein 的流处理 JobManager 是具名的分离 actor。提交进程丢失不会停止作业，但整个 Ray 集群丢失后必须基于持久检查点存储重新提交。"

msgid "Package the application"
msgstr "打包应用"

msgid ""
"Pin Klein and the tested Ray minor together. Install only the extras "
"required by the graph, on the driver and every eligible worker:"
msgstr "同时固定 Klein 和已经测试的 Ray 次版本。仅在 driver 和每个符合条件的 worker 上安装图所需的额外依赖："

msgid ""
"Connector-specific native dependencies also belong in the worker image. For "
"example, RocketMQ requires a compatible `librocketmq`; RocksDB uses "
"`rocksdict`; Serve needs `ray[serve]`, `aiohttp`, and `orjson`."
msgstr "连接器专用的原生依赖也必须包含在 worker 镜像中。例如，RocketMQ 需要兼容的 `librocketmq`；RocksDB 使用 `rocksdict`；Serve 需要 `ray[serve]`、`aiohttp` 和 `orjson`。"

msgid ""
"Build the image or runtime environment before submission. Do not install "
"dependencies dynamically inside a UDF: that makes worker startup "
"nondeterministic and can exceed deployment timeouts."
msgstr "提交前构建好镜像或运行时环境。不要在 UDF 内动态安装依赖，否则 worker 启动将不可预测，并可能超过部署超时时间。"

msgid "Connect to a cluster"
msgstr "连接集群"

msgid ""
"Initialize Ray explicitly when the application needs a remote address, "
"dashboard, metrics exporter, runtime environment, or custom resources:"
msgstr "当应用需要远程地址、仪表板、指标导出器、运行时环境或自定义资源时，请显式初始化 Ray："

msgid ""
"If Ray is not initialized, native streaming execution starts an embedded "
"local cluster. That is convenient for development but is not a production "
"deployment strategy."
msgstr "如果 Ray 尚未初始化，原生流处理执行会启动一个嵌入式本地集群。这便于开发，但不是生产部署策略。"

msgid "Submit with Ray Jobs"
msgstr "使用 Ray Jobs 提交"

msgid ""
"Keep graph construction in a normal Python entry point, for example "
"`pipeline.py`, and submit it with the Ray Jobs mechanism used by the cluster:"
msgstr "将图构建放在普通 Python 入口点（例如 `pipeline.py`）中，并使用集群采用的 Ray Jobs 机制提交："

msgid ""
"The submission process may remain attached, or it may exit after printing "
"the Klein namespace. The detached streaming actors continue running. Capture "
"the Ray Jobs submission ID, Klein namespace, source consumer identity, code "
"version, and checkpoint root in deployment metadata."
msgstr "提交流程可以保持连接，也可以在输出 Klein 命名空间后退出。分离的流处理 actor 会继续运行。请在部署元数据中记录 Ray Jobs 提交 ID、Klein 命名空间、数据源消费者身份、代码版本和检查点根目录。"

msgid ""
"For container or KubeRay deployments, put the same wheel/application "
"artifact in the head and worker images or provide an immutable Ray runtime "
"environment. Mount node-local SSD for RocksDB working state when used, and "
"provide object storage credentials through workload identity or the "
"platform's secret mechanism rather than source code."
msgstr "对于容器或 KubeRay 部署，请在 head 和 worker 镜像中放入相同的 wheel/应用制品，或提供不可变的 Ray 运行时环境。使用 RocksDB 工作状态时，请挂载节点本地 SSD；对象存储凭据应通过工作负载身份或平台的密钥机制提供，不要写入源码。"

msgid "Size resources"
msgstr "规划资源容量"

msgid ""
"Each source, transform, and sink declares `num_cpus`, `num_gpus`, and "
"`concurrency`. The streaming scheduler needs resources for all live "
"subtasks, the JobManager, checkpoint coordinator, and optional Serve client "
"actors."
msgstr "每个 Source、转换和 Sink 都会声明 `num_cpus`、`num_gpus` 和 `concurrency`。流处理调度器需要为所有活动子任务、JobManager、检查点协调器和可选的 Serve 客户端 actor 准备资源。"

msgid "Before submitting:"
msgstr "提交前："

msgid ""
"Review the plan for unexpected shuffles, fan-out, concurrency, and resource "
"requests. Placement groups are attempted by default; if the reservation "
"cannot be satisfied before its timeout, Klein falls back according to the "
"configured deployment mode. A fallback can start the job but change locality "
"and performance, so alert on deployment warnings."
msgstr "检查计划中是否存在意外的 shuffle、扇出、并发度和资源请求。默认会尝试使用 placement group；如果在超时前无法满足预留请求，Klein 会按配置的部署模式回退。回退可以启动作业，但可能改变数据局部性和性能，因此应针对部署警告设置告警。"

msgid ""
"The Ray Object Store must hold in-flight data and any hot checkpoint "
"snapshots. It is not durable storage. Size it together with `pipeline.input-"
"buffer.size`, output batching, replay-buffer limits, and the largest "
"expected state snapshot."
msgstr "Ray Object Store 必须容纳传输中的数据和所有热检查点快照。它不是持久存储。规划容量时应综合考虑 `pipeline.input-buffer.size`、输出批处理、重放缓冲区限制和预期最大的状态快照。"

msgid "Configure durable services"
msgstr "配置持久服务"

msgid "Production streaming jobs should set:"
msgstr "生产流处理作业应设置："

msgid "a shared `execution.checkpointing.dir` reachable by every worker;"
msgstr "每个 worker 都能访问的共享 `execution.checkpointing.dir`；"

msgid ""
"enough retained checkpoints to survive one corrupt or operationally bad "
"revision;"
msgstr "保留足够多的检查点，以应对一个损坏或运行效果不佳的修订版；"

msgid ""
"stable external source identities where resubmission must recover progress;"
msgstr "需要在重新提交后恢复进度时，使用稳定的外部数据源身份；"

msgid "explicit output idempotency or transactional behavior;"
msgstr "明确的输出幂等性或事务行为；"

msgid "Ray metrics export and log retention independent of worker lifetime."
msgstr "不依赖 worker 生命周期的 Ray 指标导出和日志保留。"

msgid ""
"For S3-compatible storage, pass filesystem construction settings through "
"`execution.checkpointing.storage-options`. Prefer identity-based "
"credentials. Snapshot publication redacts credential-like configuration "
"fields, but checkpoint metadata and application logs should never receive "
"raw secrets."
msgstr "对于兼容 S3 的存储，通过 `execution.checkpointing.storage-options` 传递文件系统构造设置。优先使用基于身份的凭据。快照发布会遮蔽类似凭据的配置字段，但检查点元数据和应用日志绝不能接收原始密钥。"

msgid "Operate the deployed job"
msgstr "运维已部署的作业"

msgid ""
"`attach` requires a TTY and detaches on Ctrl+C without stopping the job. "
"`stop` is cancellation, not savepoint creation. Confirm that an acceptable "
"completed checkpoint exists before an upgrade or cluster shutdown when the "
"job must be restored later."
msgstr "`attach` 需要 TTY；按 Ctrl+C 只会断开连接，不会停止作业。`stop` 表示取消，而不是创建 savepoint。如果稍后需要恢复作业，请在升级或关闭集群前确认存在可接受的已完成检查点。"

msgid "Upgrade procedure"
msgstr "升级流程"

msgid ""
"Verify the target Klein/Ray versions against [Compatibility](compatibility."
"md)."
msgstr "根据[兼容性](compatibility.md)验证目标 Klein/Ray 版本。"

msgid ""
"Wait for a completed durable checkpoint and record its exact `chk-N` URI."
msgstr "等待持久检查点完成，并记录其确切的 `chk-N` URI。"

msgid "Stop the old job and confirm its detached actors are gone."
msgstr "停止旧作业，并确认其分离 actor 已全部退出。"

msgid "Deploy the new immutable application artifact."
msgstr "部署新的不可变应用制品。"

msgid ""
"Resubmit with `execution.savepoint.path` and the original max parallelism."
msgstr "使用 `execution.savepoint.path` 和原来的最大并行度重新提交。"

msgid ""
"Validate source position, state restore, sink behavior, and a new completed "
"checkpoint before declaring success."
msgstr "验证数据源位置、状态恢复、Sink 行为以及一个新的已完成检查点，再宣布升级成功。"

msgid ""
"Alpha releases do not promise automatic checkpoint-schema migration. Test an "
"upgrade against a copy of production-shaped state before using it as the "
"only recovery path."
msgstr "Alpha 版本不承诺自动迁移检查点模式。在将升级作为唯一恢复路径前，请使用符合生产规模特征的状态副本进行测试。"

msgid "Connector-specific native dependencies also belong in the worker image. For example, RocketMQ requires a compatible `librocketmq`; RocksDB uses `rocksdict`; Serve needs `ray[serve]`, `httpx`, and `orjson`."
msgstr "连接器专用的原生依赖也必须放入 Worker 镜像。例如，RocketMQ 需要兼容的 `librocketmq`，RocksDB 使用 `rocksdict`，Serve 则需要 `ray[serve]`、`httpx` 和 `orjson`。"

msgid "The Klein Dashboard listens on `127.0.0.1:8266` by default and serves its packaged MUI/React Flow application without a Ray source checkout or a separate frontend process. Ray-owned navigation opens the configured native Ray Dashboard. When publishing either service, put both behind the cluster's normal authenticated operations proxy and pass browser-visible URLs, not loopback addresses that exist only inside a remote host. `--frontend-url` is an optional development override for testing an unbuilt UI served elsewhere."
msgstr "Klein Dashboard 默认监听 `127.0.0.1:8266`，并直接提供打包好的 MUI/React Flow 应用，无需检出 Ray 源码或运行独立前端进程。由 Ray 管理的导航会打开已配置的原生 Ray Dashboard。发布任一服务时，应将两者都置于集群常规的已认证运维代理之后，并传入浏览器可访问的 URL，而不是仅存在于远程主机内部的回环地址。`--frontend-url` 是可选的开发覆盖项，用于测试由其他位置提供、尚未构建的 UI。"
